high_descs: Turn around and go to the small black table
Grab the knife off of the table
Cut the apple on the table into three slices
Turn around and face the white table
Put the knife on the white table
Turn right and go to the black table
Grab a slice of the apple
Turn around and go to the oven
Put the apple in the pan on the bottom left stove
Grab the pan from the bottom left stove
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan with a sliced apple in it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the white table, then turn to the right to face the black table.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the black table.
Use the butter knife to slice the potato towards the back of the table.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to face the white table and the loaf of bread.
Put the butter knife down on the table and loaf of bread.
Turn to the right to face the black table.
Pick up a slice of the cut potato.
Turn to the right, go forward, then turn to the left, go to the wall, turn to the right to face the stove.
Put the potato in the pan on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the potato in it from the left side of the stove.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right, walk towards the trash can, hang a left and go to the fridge.
Put the pan containing the potato inside the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing potato in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black table next to the trash bag in the corner.
Pick up the knife behind the vase on the black table.
Cut up the potato on the black table.
Turn left and walk to the table with the bread on it.
Place the knife on top of the bread on the table.
Turn right and walk to the small black table.
Pick up a piece of the potato from the table.
Turn around and walk to the stove.
Put the piece of potato in the pot on the left.
Pick up the pot on the left.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pot in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a piece of potato in it into the fridge.
